{'type': 'tweet', 'tweet_id': '1777954879203361082', 'screen_name': 'arrogantfrfr', 'bookmarks': 2, 'favorites': 37, 'created_at': 'Wed Apr 10 07:00:50 +0000 2024', 'text': "Gut feeling is that we reprice much higher on everything sooner than later. 

I see many accounts who think we get a dip to low 60k before more up.
